[[File:Shop keeper (Lumbridge) chathead.png|left]]
The '''shop keeper''' is in charge of the [[Lumbridge General Store]] in [[Lumbridge]]. He is assisted by the [[shop assistant (Lumbridge)]]. The shop keeper plays a minor role in the [[Death to the Dorgeshuun]]. He is one of the humans [[Zanik]] meets while visiting [[Lumbridge]]. He sells her a [[Bucket|wooden bucket]], a [[Hammer|wood hammer]], and a [[newcomer map]].

